---
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';

---
<html >
<body >
  <Navigation />
  <br>
  <script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@2.5.1/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
  <div class="acctcontainer" ></div>
  <div class="text">
    <h1> Accounting Services</h1>
  </div>
<main class="acct-page">
<div class="acctcontainer">
  <div class="image">
    <img src="../images/Accounting.jpg" alt="SinghCPA" class="responsive-image">
  </div>
  <div class="text">
	<p> Accurate, timely accounting is the foundation of sound financial decision-making. At SinghCPAInc., we provide reliable and customized accounting services to individuals, startups, small businesses, and established companies across a wide range of industries.
	<p>Our goal is to give you clarity, confidence, and control over your financial information&mdash;so you can focus on running your business and planning for the future.</p>
    <br>  
  </div>
</div>
<div class="acctcontainer">
	<div class="text">
	  <h4>Our accounting services include:</h4>
	  <br>
	  <h4>Bookkeeping & General Ledger Maintenance</h4>
	  <p>
		Stay organized and audit-ready with accurate day-to-day financial tracking.
	  </p>
	  <h4>Financial Statement Preparation</h4>
	  <p>
		Clear, GAAP-compliant reports that give you insight into your business performance.	
	  </p>
	  <h4>Monthly, Quarterly & Year-End Reporting</h4>
	  <p>
		Regular reporting packages tailored to your operational and management needs.	
	  </p>
	  <h4>Account Reconciliation</h4>
	  <p>
		Ensure your records match bank, credit card, and vendor statements.	
	  </p>
	  <h4>Cash Flow & Budget Analysis</h4>
	  <p>
		Make smarter financial decisions with forecasting and variance analysis support.	
	  </p>
	  <h4>QuickBooks & Cloud Accounting Support</h4>
	  <p>
		Setup, training, and ongoing support to help you get the most from your software.	
	  </p>
	  <p>
		Whether you need full-service accounting or support for your in-house team, we tailor our services to fit your workflow and goals. 
		We combine deep expertise with the latest technology to deliver efficient,accurate, and scalable solutions.
	  </p>
		<h4>Let us take care of the numbers&mdash;so you can focus on growth.</h4>
	</div>
  </div>
</div>
</main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.astro-a {
		position: absolute;
		top: -32px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translatex(-50%);
		width: 220px;
		height: auto;
		z-index: -1;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		color: white;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: rem;
		font-weight: 100;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: left;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		color: white;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(48ch, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
	.center {
  		display: block;
  		margin-left: auto;
  		margin-right: auto;
  		width: 50%;
	}
	html {
    background-color: rgb(28, 0, 128);
    font-family: sans-serif;
  }
  .acctcontainer {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start; /* Align items to the top */
  justify-content: flex-start; /* Align content to the left */
  gap: 20px; /* Adds space between the image and text */
  flex-wrap: wrap; /* Ensures responsiveness on smaller screens */
}

.image {
  flex: 1; /* Allows the image to take up available space */
  text-align: center; /* Centers the image */
}

.responsive-image {
  max-width: 100%; /* Ensures the image doesn't exceed its container */
  height: auto; /* Maintains the aspect ratio */
  border-radius: 10px; /* Optional: Adds rounded corners */
}

.text {
  flex: 2; /* Allows the text to take up more space than the image */
  font-size: 15px;
  color: white;
  text-align: left; /* Aligns the text to the left */
}
.services-list {
  list-style: disc; /* Adds bullet points */
  padding-left: 20px; /* Adds indentation for the bullets */
  margin-top: 10px; /* Adds spacing above the list */
  color: white; /* Ensures the text color is consistent */
  font-size: 15px; /* Adjusts the font size for readability */
}

.services-list li {
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem; /* Adds spacing between list items */
}

.text h4 {
  font-size: 18px; /* Adjusts the heading size */
  font-weight: bold; /* Makes the heading bold */
  margin-bottom: 10px; /* Adds spacing below the heading */
}

.text p {
  font-size: 15px; /* Adjusts the paragraph font size */
  line-height: 1.6; /* Improves readability */
  margin-bottom: 15px; /* Adds spacing below the paragraph */
}
.acct-page.text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: white;
    text-align: left;
}

</style>